2
00:00:10,356 --> 00:00:19,061
Specifically, this further extension allows public bodies to continue holding meetings remotely without quorum of the public body physically present at the meeting location, and to provide adequate alternative access to remote meetings.

3
00:00:19,461 --> 00:00:25,564
